ActAppropriation Act No. 4, 2012-13
PrecisAppointment of DONALD BOBIASH as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Indonesia and as Canada's Ambassador and Permanent Representative to the Association of Southeast Asian Nations, in Jakarta; and as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Democratic Republic of Timor-Leste, with residence in Jakarta; and RICHARD HANLEY as High Commissioner for Canada in Saint Vincent and the Grenadines, with residence in Bridgetown.
